h3#dependencies Dependencies
p
	| To install the library you need get some dependencies and the sources files. For example, Chico Mobile depends on 
	a(href="http://zeptojs.com/") Zepto
	|  to work.
p
	| Besides that, you can add some snippets to improve the cross-browser task.


h3#sniffing Browser sniffing
p
	| We hate writting CSS hacks. Instead of hacking the code, we rather use mobile IE's conditional comments, so if you paste this code in your HTML, Chico Mobile will know how to fix the visual inconsistencies:
pre
	| <!doctype html>
	| <!--[if IEMobile 7]> <html class="no-js iem7"> <![endif]-->
	| <!--[if (gt IEMobile 7)|!(IEMobile)]><!--> <html class="no-js"> <!--<![endif]-->

h3#meta Meta tags
h4#viewport Mobile viewport optimization
p
	| Prevent mobile browsers from scaling the content in page view:
pre <meta name="HandheldFriendly" content="True" />
p
	| Control the scaling:
pre <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=0" />
p
	| Force font smoothing:
pre <meta http-equiv="cleartype" content="on" />

h4#icons Home screen icons
p
	| For non-Retina iPhone, iPod Touch, and Android 2.1+ devices:
pre <link rel="apple-touch-icon-precomposed" href="icon-57x57.png" />
p
	| For first-generation iPad:
pre <link rel="apple-touch-icon-precomposed" sizes="72x72" href="icon-72x72.png" />
p
	| For iPhone 4 with high-resolution Retina display:
pre <link rel="apple-touch-icon-precomposed" sizes="114x114" href="icon-114x114.png" />
p
	| For third generation iPad Retina Display:
pre <link rel="apple-touch-icon-precomposed" sizes="144x144" href="icon-144x144.png" />

h3#pages Pages
p Each view in your page should be identified with two attributes:
ul.ch-list
	li
		code data-page
		| : Specifies which view is it. Use 
		strong "index"
		|  as main view.
	li
		code role
		| : Describes the structure of the page, such as regions. Set it as  
		strong "region"
		| .
p So, you have to wrap all your main view into this element:
pre
	| <div data-page="index" role="region">
	| 	<!-- Your code -->
	| </div>

h3#zepto Zepto JavaScript Library
p
