p.ch-message.ch-information
	| We recommend put all the &lt;script&gt; calls at bottom of HTML page, before &lt;/body&gt; tag close.


h3#sources Which are the sources?
p
	| You only have to add the CSS, JavaScript and assets of Chico Mobile, and that's all!
form.ch-box-container(action="/versions/mobile/#{mobile.version}/chico-mobile-#{mobile.version}.zip")
	p
		input.ch-btn.ch-primary(type="submit", value="Download v#{mobile.version}")
		|  or 
		a(href="http://github.com/mercadolibre/chico-mobile", target="_blank") fork on GitHub
		| .

p
	| Make sure to add the stylesheet call into the 
	code &lt;head&gt;
	|  tag.
pre
	| <link rel="stylesheet" href="chico-mobile-x.x.x.css" />
p
	| And you should add the JavaScript at bottom of page, before 
	code &lt;/body&gt;
	|  tag close and 
	strong after Zepto script call
	| .
pre
	| <script src="chico-mobile-x.x.x.js"></script>
p
	| Assets (images and fonts) are into the 
	strong zip file
	|  that you 
	a(href="#") download
	| . Put assets on a folder into your project and link to files within stylesheet code.

